sub_title: •Sound Engineer • Music Producer • Songwriter • Sound Designer • Mixing & Mastering
summary:
Dany Beats is a Rwandan based musician, music producer and audio engineer from Kigali/Rwanda.

His skillset includes songwriting, arranging, producing, conducting; piano/ keys, drums, bass, guitars, vocals; recording, editing, mixing, mastering; live performance and live sound.

Having been involved in countless single, EP and album productions from a wide range of musical genres, his productions have been warmly embraced by the public, received good press in music magazines and achieved airplay on both national and international radio stations.
Beyond that, Dany has been a record producer since the age of eleven.
In 2019, he released Platinum singles as executive producer such as Twifunze by Sintex, Special by Kevin Skaa, Kugasima by Bushali among others. The songs were covered in multiple large-scale newspapers, magazines, blogs and radio programmes and they were nominated for a radio award on 'KissFM' including him as the best summer award producer 2019 one of the largest radio stations in Rwanda.
